# Tests

## Scope

WebRTC SFU integration tests under `tests/server/sfu/`. Each test file covers one aspect: signaling, ICE, track lifecycle, media transmission, error scenarios.

## Doc Lookup

Test file `tests/server/sfu/webrtc-ice.test.ts` → doc `docs-src/tests/server/sfu/webrtc-ice.md` (drop `.test` from stem).

Helper: `tests/server/helpers.ts` → `docs-src/tests/server/helpers.md`

## Conventions

- No test runner configured in root `package.json` — verify how tests are executed before adding new ones
- Tests interact with SFU module directly; read `docs-src/server/src/sfu.md` for SFU internals
